      "content": {
        "title": "Key microscope ideas",
        "content": "Magnification = image size / actual size. Resolution is how clearly two close points can be separated. Electron microscopes have higher resolution than light microscopes."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "BIO-101-1B-worked",
      "type": "worked-example",
      "order": 3,
